source.name: Registered Vacant Property in Washington DC
source.description: Registered Vacant Property locations. The dataset contains locations and attributes of registered vacant properties from the Office of Tax and Revenue (OTR), created as part of the Citywide Data Warehouse Program (CityDW) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies.
